  Source:
    Title: Harijan
    Editor: Mohandas Gandhi
    Locus:
      Date: 18 Mar 1939
---
Fasting is a potent weapon in the Satyagraha armoury. It cannot be taken by
everyone. Mere physical capacity to take it is no qualification for it. It
is of no use without a living faith in God. It should never be a mechanical
effort nor a mere imitation. It must come from the depth of one's soul.
